'''四碘化钽'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为TaI<sub>4</sub>，它可由[[五碘化钽|五碘化钽]]和[[钽|钽]]的还原反应制得<ref name=Robert />，若以[[吡啶|吡啶]]为还原剂，则会得到加合物TaI<sub>4</sub>(py)<sub>2</sub><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=2|issue=3|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=1963-06|pages=547–551|doi=10.1021/ic50007a030|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ic50007a030|title=The Preparation of Tantalum(IV) Bromide, Tantalum(IV) Iodide, and Pyridine Adducts of the Tantalum(IV) Halides|accessdate=2021-03-24|author=R. E. McCarley, J. C. Boatman}}</ref>。它溶于水得到绿色溶液，但在空气中放置颜色褪去，并产生白色沉淀。<ref name=Robert>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=80|issue=12|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1958-06|pages=2952–2953|doi=10.1021/ja01545a011|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01545a011|title=Preparation and X-ray Study of Some Tantalum Halides|accessdate=2021-03-24|author=Robert F. Rolsten}}</ref>

它是[[三斜晶系|三斜晶系]]晶体，[[空间群|空间群]]P{{overline|1}}，具有Ta<sub>4</sub>I<sub>16</sub>结构。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=634|issue=5|language=de|date=2008-05|pages=825–828|doi=10.1002/zaac.200700529|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/zaac.200700529|title=Tantalum(IV) Iodide, TaI4: A Molecular Solid Consisting of Dimers of Dimers, Ta4I16|accessdate=2021-03-24|author=Gerd Meyer, Rafal Wiglusz, Ingo Pantenburg, Anja-Verena Mudring}}</ref>

